<body>
    <h1>Components and Templates Documentation</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"4ab92a43ec02" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumenta=
tion-Overview">Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9cc0fc57a552">The Mews Automation platform enables propertie=
s to build no-code workflows that react to events in Mews and perform actio=
ns automatically. It is powered by the <strong>Automation Gateway</strong> =
(.NET API) and <strong>Appmixer</strong> (visual workflow engine). This pag=
e serves as the index for all component and flow documentation.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"0d2f57efbb43" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumentation-Tri=
ggers">Triggers</h2>
<p local-id=3D"fec59fc1fa89">Triggers start a workflow when something happe=
ns in Mews.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"5a=
cf8e71-afe7-440a-a08f-24774b95f18b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"79fcf8c6-07be-478b-99e0-11ab8b2bf8b6">
<th data-local-id=3D"8613cd5b-8a1f-42e0-905c-ae7c25cb5a64" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"58f964f8cb4f">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"1d68e5e3-17a3-4ac5-81ba-1679c9e5478b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5edce8de09e3">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f04790fe-fa45-4e02-b525-0d36de428468">
<td data-local-id=3D"af679692-8c9f-40f2-ac7a-a2e3bb1eca05" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f115ac186fe3">Guest Profile Created</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f8d96740-426b-493a-9562-5eebfdc8f411" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e733d22325ec">Fires when a new guest profile is created, out=
putting guest details such as name, contact info, nationality, language, an=
d loyalty code.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4543ac76-5772-4fc9-adbd-2e8cb4fdd7b8">
<td data-local-id=3D"5e1f1499-9829-4dee-a1b0-051878324665" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e12dadeee88e">Reservation Created</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a65d4ddb-e9d4-42b9-8f30-5725366cf4f8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4e6ea1aa4ac1">Fires when a new reservation is created, outpu=
tting reservation and guest details including confirmation number, origin, =
assigned space, and rate.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b3a33a28-b8d8-4aa5-909b-5ba648cce9c0">
<td data-local-id=3D"1725735d-e2ff-41cf-849d-1a91499e7f10" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"da83630c97f2">Reservation Checked In</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a331279b-0d1b-483d-95c3-c3a18f7abea9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"73120b129e96">Fires when a guest checks in, outputting compr=
ehensive reservation and guest details including room assignment and dates.=
</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"b4405f898809" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumentation-Act=
ions">Actions</h2>
<p local-id=3D"49d2f8e3b75b">Actions perform an operation inside a workflow=
 =E2=80=94 retrieving data, modifying reservations, or communicating with g=
uests.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"631e300c954b" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumentation-Gue=
st&amp;ReservationOperations">Guest &amp; Reservation Operations</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"fa=
da530b-e13f-493f-a507-9c6ccf225382" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"55ba10da-0873-407d-9d7d-6ae296829536">
<th data-local-id=3D"3989c7bb-0a97-4bc2-91e3-ea2246de9427" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f5df0d8dbbb5">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"2196df12-4017-49a2-b3a6-8a96503f39cd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7c7191eab1b3">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3a5557ee-0651-43df-813d-d04ebac20bc8">
<td data-local-id=3D"e864b65e-f24a-418c-ad89-47e662213f35" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"158d81662024">Add Note to Guest Profile</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c687e4af-8684-40fd-987c-999676cb6454" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aa92097aa2ed">Adds a categorised text note (e.g. Housekeepin=
g, Complaints) to a guest profile.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"56f68bca-7fc9-41a7-844c-99f3c676a6b1">
<td data-local-id=3D"03a9a988-2d77-4543-8fe7-736404edb6b0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b1131ec6a7f">Add Note to Reservation</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bb449a60-b8fb-4401-842d-df7e6b4654cd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a2d99a7816dc">Adds a note to one or more reservations at onc=
e, useful for group bookings or operational remarks.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"94fbed2b-9fa4-4365-ba24-d2fac0b69399">
<td data-local-id=3D"5f6863b0-674c-4d31-996b-59e5341fae8b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5848ea42aabc">Add Product to Reservation</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8db910d3-83e1-40ed-bfe5-9d472ae061e3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74b3518cd145">Adds a product (charge) to a reservation with =
configurable quantity and date range =E2=80=94 e.g. breakfast, parking, lat=
e checkout.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fc0b10f1-b8a3-46ef-96dd-2d53f195a747">
<td data-local-id=3D"38317479-d5fc-4dae-8ccd-9ee28c966585" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af42447156c8">Upgrade Assigned Room Category</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"83d66369-8001-4616-a14c-4d3406252630" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b2710c2d9d5">Upgrades a guest to a higher room category bas=
ed on configurable upgrade paths, availability, and buffer settings.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"54ba92bf-247a-41a4-a8cd-4742f5a69bad">
<td data-local-id=3D"7c3f1236-9076-4798-b152-3f627bb4e94a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"27b5ae077966">Send SMS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"80bd59fc-4dc2-4905-ada8-5910ca70c846" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"db5f628fcda2">Sends an SMS to a guest, optionally linked to =
a reservation.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3aadf43f-f369-4450-92e8-f196c6e1af4e">
<td data-local-id=3D"3aa83e6f-21b0-4888-8a58-9c965a882371" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ac4ea49a932e">Add Task</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"cc52d332-59c7-4e5c-9475-4bd95aa294c7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"738e3c25be64">Creates a task in Mews Operations with a deadl=
ine, optional description, department, and reservation link.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"b7d6032bd55a" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumentation-Dat=
aRetrieval&amp;Filtering">Data Retrieval &amp; Filtering</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"42=
9019be-6110-4504-a4ed-99df4bee6f23" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"87c97c43-e45a-45b4-baab-884c15ec60c8">
<th data-local-id=3D"46d2a9c3-2a22-4559-a457-546e7fc3ceb8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0a8571d8793c">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ac04281a-348b-43e7-bfe9-6219e59c0a52" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"24c29d15eb70">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dbba837d-32c1-465a-b98c-49244d257970">
<td data-local-id=3D"cbbec171-feb2-4808-a5d6-8223e8db13e4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3f147db81bb3">Get Eligible Arrivals</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"99bfa84a-e78a-448b-8ef2-64a48efad101" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f6228b6e357">Retrieves confirmed reservations arriving on a=
 given date, with optional loyalty, behavioural, and rate filters.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2d576d32-de28-4b4c-b04e-4dc1e5fe6e92">
<td data-local-id=3D"fe8e4afe-fc54-4add-b614-b4d8d56ca12a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d5e3f6b91242">Get Occupancy / Check Occupancy</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2839b597-f464-46ee-8d93-d7ad64e4a9a4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8adf9bd6fd03">Returns the occupancy percentage for a date. <=
em>Check Occupancy</em> additionally compares it against a threshold for co=
nditional branching.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"60e48037-88cb-40c6-bade-c30dd0b4a41f">
<td data-local-id=3D"05052c78-a262-47dc-8353-d393aad5c069" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"95ee7e163327">Get Products / Get Products for Reservations /=
 Get Compatible Products</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6015c8ba-8392-47f6-9eac-a66be6325f6a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"73b79c3a8da5">Retrieve orderable products =E2=80=94 property=
-wide, per reservation, or filtered for compatibility.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"76c47603-d32c-44c2-8ce2-c59bc2bf8d61">
<td data-local-id=3D"fcc274b5-1a8a-4830-9a87-eb8d5597f87e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"34bea68bcd5f">Get Services</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"25c1c70f-4c7f-4810-ba7d-3e30d340b6ad" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"64fa9d6c2e46">Lists active (optionally bookable-only) servic=
es at the property.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"388ca089-daed-4b35-8444-ee4c6557d97b">
<td data-local-id=3D"a1843bbb-84ce-4a51-b9a4-08a4a416a26d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c6fef98a67ab">Get Space Categories</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"71afe445-5962-4623-9a72-264e748e7d84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"caa7da2c1c11">Lists room/space categories, optionally filter=
ed by service.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5fd3e280-f563-4f10-b1fa-305b10d50f56">
<td data-local-id=3D"948a9eca-7304-4e4e-b48f-91a01e9226ba" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a9c75295a04a">Get Rates</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bc0010ff-d6c5-4e6c-9ba4-b8190c4633ac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"696d4f44e950">Lists enabled rates across bookable services.<=
/p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4219f1b4-e48d-4e13-8628-3f92bfb095e9">
<td data-local-id=3D"6d06f9a4-f326-4570-b58f-8c82e36848eb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3a7149089de1">Get Departments</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"14217974-6ee6-4c6b-a000-486d11148e70" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"09432dc2b3bd">Lists active departments for task routing.</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"025a6928-3f52-4192-b81e-90c28eee839f">
<td data-local-id=3D"531b9a8d-0476-4821-86b0-ef6d3bf431ad" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e6a70210f0b8">Get Loyalty Programs / Get Loyalty Tiers</p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ad6294ea-8bc3-4fbb-ae15-ec42939926d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"95f2620d5af7">Lists loyalty programs and their tiers for seg=
mentation and filtering.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"16681ee31b62" id=3D"ComponentsandTemplatesDocumentation-Exa=
mpleFlows">Example Flows</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0ee23105d01f">End-to-end automation recipes that combine the=
 components above.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"cf=
8cebde-b965-44ec-a3e4-614a85017f04" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3c209448-bc03-44fe-8b68-304ee7337f86">
<th data-local-id=3D"ecc5f5e1-f99e-429f-8269-f2cbfa4e4204" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"57217a73cf98">Flow</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f022349d-3603-4a1f-a4ce-e06e32d427ce" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d6c405faf2ee">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"77b04ece-6175-4b5a-ab59-405b00f029a8">
<td data-local-id=3D"29d0934c-6199-4832-8254-6e25dca1f0aa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0d31b2214398">Upgrade Room for Loyalty Members</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3d6d1fae-ddb3-4fc9-a5e9-1bebac87de87" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4239433b04fb">Runs daily: identifies arriving guests (with o=
ptional loyalty/behavioural filters), checks occupancy, attempts room upgra=
des with availability buffers, sends SMS to upgraded guests, and notes fail=
ed upgrades.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"63a810a6-d64a-48a3-9959-66e090fe26d2">
<td data-local-id=3D"c0b1f133-ff16-4e55-a9fb-9947c4d497db" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"741403a667c4">Welcome Gift for VIP Guests</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"16bfb7b5-3ccb-4d33-962d-f726afa4e765" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"149f22318197">Runs daily: identifies arriving guests, checks=
 product compatibility, creates staff tasks for welcome gifts, and sends SM=
S to notify guests.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
